{"title_page": "Molau", "text_new": "{{Infobox German location\n|type = Ortsteil\n|Municipality = [[Molauer Land]]\n|image_photo       = \n|image_coa            = kein\n|coordinates       = {{coord|51|2|59|N|11|46|59|E|format=dms|display=inline,title}}\n|image_plan          = \n|state        = Sachsen-Anhalt\n|district         = Burgenlandkreis\n|elevation              = 263\n|area            = 13.39\n|population         = 551\n|Stand             = 2006-12-31\n|postal_code               = 06618\n|area_code           = 036694\n|licence               = BLK\n|website           = [http://www.vgem-wethautal.de/ www.vgem-wethautal.de]\n}}\n\n'''Molau''' is a village and a former municipality in the [[Burgenlandkreis]] district, in [[Saxony-Anhalt]], [[Germany]]. Since 1 January 2010, it is part of the municipality [[Molauer Land]].\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Villages in Saxony-Anhalt]]\n[[Category:Duchy of Saxe-Meiningen]]\n[[Category:Bezirk Halle]]\n\n\n{{Burgenlandkreis-geo-stub}}\n\n[[it:Molau]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox German location\n|type = Ortsteil\n|Municipality = [[Molauer Land]]\n|image_photo       = \n|image_coa            = kein\n|coordinates       = {{coord|51|2|59|N|11|46|59|E|format=dms|display=inline,title}}\n|image_plan          = \n|state        = Sachsen-Anhalt\n|district         = Burgenlandkreis\n|elevation              = 263\n|area            = 13.39\n|population         = 551\n|Stand             = 2006-12-31\n|postal_code               = 06618\n|area_code           = 036694\n|licence               = BLK\n|website           = [http://www.vgem-wethautal.de/ www.vgem-wethautal.de]\n}}\n\n'''Molau''' is a village and a former municipality in the [[Burgenlandkreis]] district, in [[Saxony-Anhalt]], [[Germany]]. Since 1 January 2010, it is part of the municipality [[Molauer Land]].\n\n[[Category:Villages in Saxony-Anhalt]]\n[[Category:Duchy of Saxe-Meiningen]]\n[[Category:Bezirk Halle]]\n\n{{Burgenlandkreis-geo-stub}}\n\n[[it:Molau]]\n", "